              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            "& when (@fullWidth)": {
              ".container-fluid": {
                "padding": "0 50px",
                "margin": "0",
                "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                  "padding": "0 20px"
                },
                ".row": {
                  "padding": "0"
                }
              }
            },
            ".container": {
              "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                "padding": "0 20px"
              }
            },
            ".title-wrapper": {
              ".logo-wrap": {
                "margin-bottom": "30px",
                "@media (max-width: 768px)": {
                  "margin-bottom": "16px"
                },
                "img": {
                  "display": "inline-flex",
                  "width": "70px",
                  "height": "70px",
                  "object-fit": "contain",
                  "border-radius": "100%"
                }
              },
              ".title-wrap": {
                ".mbr-section-title": {
                  "margin-bottom": "30px"
                }
              }
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "color": "#ffffff"
            },
            ".mbr-section-title, .mbr-section-btn, .logo-wrap": {
              "text-align": "center",
              "color": "#000000"
            },
            ".mbr-section-title, .mbr-section-btn, .logo-wrap DIV": {
              "text-align": "justify"
            }
          },
          "_name": "content4",
          "_sourceTheme": "vibem5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content4 vibem5\" group=\"Content\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen, 'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Logo\" name=\"showLogo\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#000000\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-12\">\n                <div class=\"title-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"logo-wrap\" mbr-if=\"showLogo\">\n                        <img src=\"../_images/logo.png\" alt=\"Mobirise\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"title-wrap\">\n                        <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title, .mbr-section-btn, .logo-wrap\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><div>Success is a concept that means different things to different people, but for Robert Susa, it has a very precise and meaningful definition, particularly when it comes to inventors. As the President and Owner of InventHelp, one of North America’s longest-standing invention support organizations, Susa has spent decades cultivating a philosophy of integrity, transparency, and accountability. His professional journey has been driven by a deep passion for empowering independent inventors, providing them with the tools, knowledge, and guidance necessary to navigate the complex world of invention.</div><br><div>\n</div><div>From the moment inventors engage with InventHelp, Susa emphasizes that success is not merely about bringing an idea to market but about nurturing a creator’s confidence and vision. He believes that structured support, grounded in ethical practices, forms the foundation upon which an inventor can thrive. Whether it involves helping clients refine their concepts, access patent referrals, or prepare professional marketing materials, Susa ensures that inventors receive guidance that is both practical and principled.</div><br><div>\n</div><div>Beyond his professional role, Robert Susa champions education and opportunity as integral components of success. He actively supports scholarships and initiatives that promote lifelong learning, creativity, and professional growth. For Susa, success is about creating an environment where inventors can not only pursue their ideas but do so with clarity, assurance, and a sense of purpose. By cultivating ethical service and continuous improvement within InventHelp, he has defined a model for supporting inventors that balances vision with responsibility.</div><br><div>\n</div><div>At its core, Susa’s definition of success centers on empowerment. He views success as helping inventors make informed decisions, understand the market realities, and gain the confidence to take their ideas from concept to reality. By placing integrity and transparency at the forefront, Susa ensures that every inventor he works with feels respected, supported, and equipped for the challenges and triumphs of the invention journey.\n</div><div><br></div></h2>\n                    </div>\n                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\">\n                        <a class=\"btn btn-primary-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                            Start Now\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "ujl6WEaKIQ",
          "_anchor": "content4-3",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "_name": "article03",
          "_sourceTheme": "promotionm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article03 promotionm5\" group=\"Article\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Label\" name=\"showLabel\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Icon\" name=\"showIcon\" checked condition=\"showLabel\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/promotionm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#0e0533\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/promotionm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-10\">\n                <div class=\"content-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"row content-wrap\" mbr-class=\"{'flex-row-reverse' : reverseContent}\">\n                        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-3 card\">\n                            <div class=\"label-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showLabel\">\n                                <div class=\"label-wrap\">\n                                    <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                                        <span mbr-icon class=\"card-icon mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-more-horizontal mobi-mbri\" data-app-selector=\".card-icon\" style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); fill: rgb(31, 31, 31);\"></span>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-label mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-label, .label-wrapper\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                                        Elevate\n                                    </p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-9 card\">\n                            <div class=\"text-wrapper\">\n                                <div class=\"title-wrapper\">\n                                    <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title, .title-wrapper, .links-wrapper\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Robert Susa: Fueling Creativity And Success</b><br></h2>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"text-wrap\">\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .text-wrap\">For Robert Susa, financial success is only one aspect of an inventor’s journey. He believes that the true measure of achievement lies in the ability of inventors to transform ideas into tangible solutions that address real-world needs. Success is about fostering creativity, encouraging problem-solving, and nurturing a mindset of continuous learning. Inventors who emerge from Susa’s guidance are not only better prepared to navigate business complexities but also more confident in their ability to innovate responsibly. This holistic approach separates fleeting achievements from sustainable, meaningful success.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"links-wrapper\">\n                                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Brand Strategy\n                                        </a>\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Digital Marketing\n                                        </a>\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Content Creation\n                                        </a>\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Performance Analytics\n                                        </a>\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Social Media\n                                        </a>\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Paid Advertising\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            ".content-wrap": {
              "margin": "0 -50px",
              ".card": {
                "padding": "0 50px",
                "&:last-child": {
                  "justify-content": "flex-end"
                }
              },
              ".label-wrapper": {
                "margin-bottom": "20px",
                ".label-wrap": {
                  "display": "inline-flex",
                  "flex-wrap": "wrap",
                  "align-items": "center",
                  "gap": "8px",
                  ".iconfont-wrapper": {
                    "display": "flex",
                    ".mbr-iconfont": {
                      "display": "inline-flex",
