          },
          "_name": "content4",
          "_sourceTheme": "vibem5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content4 vibem5\" group=\"Content\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen, 'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Logo\" name=\"showLogo\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#000000\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-12\">\n                <div class=\"title-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"logo-wrap\" mbr-if=\"showLogo\">\n                        <img src=\"../_images/logo.png\" alt=\"Mobirise\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"title-wrap\">\n                        <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title, .mbr-section-btn, .logo-wrap\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><div>Leadership is often discussed in terms of vision, influence, or innovation, but accountability is the quiet force that sustains all three. In the case of Robert Susa, accountability is not a supporting trait—it is the backbone of his leadership philosophy. With decades of experience guiding inventors through complex decision-making and long-term development, his approach reflects a rare blend of discipline, transparency, and respect for the people he serves.</div><br><div>\n</div><div>As President and Owner of InventHelp, Robert Susa has spent years shaping an organizational culture where responsibility is shared, expectations are clear, and ethical conduct is non-negotiable. His leadership journey is not defined by flashy promises or abstract ideals, but by consistent follow-through and a commitment to doing right by inventors who entrust their ideas to professional guidance. This mindset has helped establish trust not only within his organization but also across the broader invention services space.</div><br><div>\n</div><div>What sets Robert apart is his ability to translate accountability into practical systems. Rather than treating it as a buzzword, he embeds it into communication, service delivery, and long-term strategy. Inventors are encouraged to understand the realities of the invention process, make informed decisions, and take ownership of their progress while receiving structured, professional support.</div><br><div>\n</div><div>This blog explores how accountability shapes Robert Susa’s leadership approach, influences organizational culture, strengthens inventor relationships, and supports sustainable innovation. By examining his methods and values, readers gain insight into why accountability remains one of the most powerful tools in principled leadership.\n</div><div><br></div></h2>\n                    </div>\n                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\">\n                        <a class=\"btn btn-primary-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                            Start Now\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "v9v2DkL5Z6",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {},
          "_anchor": "content4-65"
        },
        {
          "_name": "article03",
          "_sourceTheme": "promotionm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article03 promotionm5\" group=\"Article\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Label\" name=\"showLabel\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Icon\" name=\"showIcon\" checked condition=\"showLabel\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/promotionm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#0e0533\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/promotionm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-10\">\n                <div class=\"content-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"row content-wrap\" mbr-class=\"{'flex-row-reverse' : reverseContent}\">\n                        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-3 card\">\n                            <div class=\"label-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showLabel\">\n                                <div class=\"label-wrap\">\n                                    <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                                        <span mbr-icon class=\"card-icon mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-more-horizontal mobi-mbri\" data-app-selector=\".card-icon\" style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); fill: rgb(31, 31, 31);\"></span>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-label mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-label, .label-wrapper\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                                        Elevate\n                                    </p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-9 card\">\n                            <div class=\"text-wrapper\">\n                                <div class=\"title-wrapper\">\n                                    <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title, .title-wrapper, .links-wrapper\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Robert Susa: Inspiring Innovation Everywhere</b><br></h2>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"text-wrap\">\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .text-wrap\">At the heart of Robert Susa’s leadership philosophy is a belief that integrity must be lived, not declared. Accountability serves as the mechanism that turns ethical intent into daily practice. By holding himself and his organization to clear standards, he reinforces credibility in an industry where trust is essential.<br>\n<br>Rather than positioning leadership as authority over others, Robert frames it as responsibility to others. This perspective reshapes how decisions are made. Accountability means asking hard questions, acknowledging limitations, and ensuring that commitments are realistic and transparent. When expectations are grounded in honesty, outcomes tend to align more closely with reality.<br>\n<br>This foundation allows leadership to remain steady even when challenges arise. Accountability creates a stabilizing effect because it encourages proactive problem-solving instead of reactive explanations. For Robert, leadership integrity is inseparable from accountability because one cannot exist without the other.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"links-wrapper\">\n                                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Brand Strategy\n                                        </a>\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Digital Marketing\n                                        </a>\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Content Creation\n                                        </a>\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Performance Analytics\n                                        </a>\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Social Media\n                                        </a>\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Paid Advertising\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
