          "_name": "content4",
          "_sourceTheme": "vibem5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content4 vibem5\" group=\"Content\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen, 'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Logo\" name=\"showLogo\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#000000\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-12\">\n                <div class=\"title-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"logo-wrap\" mbr-if=\"showLogo\">\n                        <img src=\"../_images/logo.png\" alt=\"Mobirise\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"title-wrap\">\n                        <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title, .mbr-section-btn, .logo-wrap\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><div>Robert Susa is a seasoned business leader whose professional journey has been defined by a deep respect for innovation and the individuals behind it. As President and Owner of InventHelp, he has spent decades working closely with independent inventors, guiding them through one of the most complex and emotionally charged paths in business: transforming an idea into a viable opportunity. His leadership style reflects a rare balance of strategic insight and genuine empathy, allowing inventors to feel both supported and informed from the very beginning.</div><br><div>\n</div><div>Throughout his career, Robert Susa has emphasized that clarity is not a luxury in invention services, it is a responsibility. He understands that inventors often arrive with excitement, uncertainty, and high expectations. Rather than allowing confusion to cloud the process, he has built systems and communication frameworks that prioritize understanding at every stage. This focus on transparency has become a defining characteristic of the organization he leads.</div><br><div>\n</div><div>Drawing from extensive experience in business development and organizational communications, Robert Susa has helped shape an approach that removes ambiguity from service expectations. Each interaction is designed to ensure inventors know what services are offered, how those services work, and what outcomes can realistically be anticipated. This clarity not only protects inventors but also empowers them to make confident, informed decisions.</div><br><div>\n</div><div>At the heart of his philosophy is a belief that trust grows when information flows freely. Robert Susa’s commitment to ethical engagement and honest dialogue has reinforced InventHelp’s reputation as an organization where expectations are set thoughtfully, explained clearly, and respected consistently.\n</div><div><br></div></h2>\n                    </div>\n                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\">\n                        <a class=\"btn btn-primary-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                            Start Now\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "v9v2DWDCA4",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {},
          "_anchor": "content4-6g"
        },
        {
          "_name": "article03",
          "_sourceTheme": "promotionm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article03 promotionm5\" group=\"Article\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Label\" name=\"showLabel\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Icon\" name=\"showIcon\" checked condition=\"showLabel\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/promotionm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#0e0533\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/promotionm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-10\">\n                <div class=\"content-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"row content-wrap\" mbr-class=\"{'flex-row-reverse' : reverseContent}\">\n                        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-3 card\">\n                            <div class=\"label-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showLabel\">\n                                <div class=\"label-wrap\">\n                                    <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                                        <span mbr-icon class=\"card-icon mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-more-horizontal mobi-mbri\" data-app-selector=\".card-icon\" style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); fill: rgb(31, 31, 31);\"></span>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-label mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-label, .label-wrapper\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                                        Elevate\n                                    </p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-9 card\">\n                            <div class=\"text-wrapper\">\n                                <div class=\"title-wrapper\">\n                                    <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title, .title-wrapper, .links-wrapper\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Robert Susa: A Leadership Philosophy Rooted In Transparency</b><br></h2>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"text-wrap\">\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .text-wrap\">One of the most important ways Robert Susa ensures clarity in service expectations is through a leadership philosophy that places transparency above all else. Rather than relying on vague promises or abstract language, he advocates for straightforward explanations that reflect real processes and real outcomes. This approach helps eliminate misunderstandings before they can take root.<br>\n<br>Under his guidance, clarity begins with mindset. Services are not presented as guarantees but as structured opportunities that require participation, patience, and informed decision-making. By establishing this tone early, Robert Susa creates an environment where inventors feel respected rather than persuaded. The result is a healthier, more productive relationship built on mutual understanding.<br>\n<br>This transparency also extends internally. Teams are trained to communicate consistently, ensuring that inventors receive the same clear message regardless of who they speak with. That consistency reinforces trust and allows expectations to remain aligned throughout the entire engagement.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"links-wrapper\">\n                                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Brand Strategy\n                                        </a>\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Digital Marketing\n                                        </a>\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Content Creation\n                                        </a>\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Performance Analytics\n                                        </a>\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Social Media\n                                        </a>\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Paid Advertising\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_styles": {
