              "position": "relative",
              "justify-content": "center",
              "padding": "50px 10px",
              "overflow": "hidden",
              "margin": "0",
              "& when (@showBorder)": {
                "border": "1px solid @border",
                "border-radius": "10px"
              },
              "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                "padding": "85px 8px"
              }
            },
            ".title-wrapper": {
              ".mbr-section-subtitle": {
                "margin-bottom": "25px"
              },
              ".mbr-section-title": {
                "margin-bottom": "50px"
              }
            },
            ".text-wrapper": {
              "padding": "0 30%",
              "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                "padding": "0"
              },
              ".mbr-text": {
                "margin-bottom": "0"
              }
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "color": "#ffffff"
            },
            ".mbr-section-subtitle": {
              "color": "#ffffff"
            },
            ".mbr-text": {
              "color": "#000000"
            },
            ".mbr-section-title, .title-wrapper": {
              "color": "#000000"
            }
          },
          "_name": "content5",
          "_sourceTheme": "deepm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content5 deepm5\" group=\"Content\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen, 'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Border\" name=\"showBorder\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Border Color\" value=\"#521825\" name=\"border\" condition=\"showBorder\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/deepm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/deepm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.7\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-12\">\n                <div class=\"title-wrapper\">\n                    <h3 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\">\n                        <b>01 INVENTORE NOBIS</b>\n                    </h3>\n                    <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title, .title-wrapper\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Setting Expectations From The Very First Conversation</b></h2>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"text-wrapper\">\n                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\">Clarity does not happen by accident, and Robert Susa understands that the first interaction often shapes an inventor’s entire experience. From the initial conversation onward, service expectations are explained in plain language, without unnecessary jargon or inflated claims. This early clarity helps inventors understand both the scope and purpose of each service offered.<br>\n<br>Rather than overwhelming individuals with information, the process is paced thoughtfully. Each step builds on the last, allowing inventors to absorb details gradually while still maintaining a clear overall picture. This measured approach reflects Robert Susa’s understanding that clarity improves when people are given space to process and ask questions.<br>\n<br>By setting expectations early, inventors can evaluate whether the services align with their goals. This openness encourages confidence and reinforces the idea that informed participation is a key part of any successful invention journey.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "v9v2DYSAKc",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {},
          "_anchor": "content5-6i"
        },
        {
          "_name": "article04",
          "_sourceTheme": "inspirem5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"inspirem5 article4\" group=\"Article\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video'&&bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"10\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/inspirem5/components/_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#0e0533\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/inspirem5/components/_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.7\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"title col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\"><b>Structured Communication That Eliminates Confusion</b></h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle align-center mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><div><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem; letter-spacing: 0px;\">A major factor in ensuring clarity is the structured communication model developed under <a href=\"index.html\" class=\"text-primary\"><b>Robert Susa’s leadership</b></a>. Information is delivered through organized materials, guided conversations, and clearly defined service descriptions. This structure minimizes ambiguity and ensures inventors always know where they are in the process.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Each phase is explained with purpose. Inventors are informed about what will happen next, why it matters, and how it contributes to their overall objectives. This step-by-step clarity reduces uncertainty and keeps expectations grounded in reality rather than assumption.</div><br><div>\n</div><div>Because communication is consistent and intentional, inventors are less likely to feel lost or unsure. Instead, they experience a steady progression that reflects both professionalism and respect for their time and investment.\n</div><div><br></div></h4>\n                <div class=\"mbr-section-btn align-center\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\">\n                    <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\">LEARN MORE</a>\n                    <a class=\"btn btn-primary-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\">LIVE DEMO</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_styles": {
            "& when not (@fullScreen)": {
              "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
              "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            ".mbr-section-subtitle": {
              "color": "#ffffff"
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "color": "#ffffff"
            }
          },
          "_cid": "v9v2DZZI3B",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {},
          "_anchor": "article04-6j"
        },
        {
          "_name": "article01",
          "_sourceTheme": "renderm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article01 renderm5\" group=\"Article\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Label\" name=\"showLabel\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Label BG\" value=\"#f7f7f7\" name=\"labelBg\" condition=\"showLabel\" selected>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/renderm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/renderm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 justify-content-center\">\n                <div class=\"content-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"content-wrap\">\n                        <div class=\"label-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showLabel\">\n                            <p class=\"mbr-label mbr-fonts-style card-wrap little-radius\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-label, .label-wrapper\">\n                                Creative Cuts\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n                        <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Aligning Services With Realistic Outcomes</b></h2>\n                        <div class=\"text-wrapper\">\n                            <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .text-wrapper\">Another way Robert Susa ensures clarity in service expectations is by aligning services with realistic outcomes. Rather than framing invention support as a shortcut to success, the focus remains on preparation, presentation, and opportunity. This honest framing allows inventors to understand the value of each service without misinterpreting its purpose.<br>\n<br>Services such as patent referrals, prototype modeling, and professional presentation materials are explained as tools—not guarantees. This distinction is critical. It allows inventors to appreciate the role these services play while maintaining realistic expectations about what comes next.<br>\n<br>By consistently reinforcing this message, Robert Susa helps inventors stay grounded. That clarity protects both their confidence and their long-term engagement, creating a more positive experience overall.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">\n                            <a class=\"btn btn-black\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                Create video\n                            </a>\n                            <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                View more\n                            </a>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            ".content-wrap": {
              ".label-wrapper": {
                "margin-bottom": "16px",
                ".mbr-label": {
                  "padding": "2px 12px",
                  "margin-bottom": "0",
                  "display": "inline-block",
                  "background-color": "@labelBg"
                }
              },
              ".mbr-section-title": {
                "margin-bottom": "24px",
                "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                  "margin-bottom": "16px"
                }
              },
              ".text-wrapper": {
                ".mbr-text": {
                  "display": "inline-block",
                  "width": "50%",
                  "margin-bottom": "0",
                  "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                    "width": "100%"
                  }
                }
              },
              ".mbr-section-btn": {
                "margin-top": "32px",
                "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                  "margin-top": "14px"
                }
              }
            },
            ".mbr-label, .label-wrapper": {
              "color": "#000000",
              "text-align": "center"
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "color": "#000000"
            },
            ".mbr-text, .text-wrapper": {
              "color": "#000000",
              "text-align": "center"
            },
            ".mbr-section-title, .mbr-section-btn": {
              "text-align": "center"
            }
          },
          "_cid": "v9v2E15DlV",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {},
          "_anchor": "article01-6k"
        },
        {
          "_name": "aarticle2",
          "_sourceTheme": "algom5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article2 algom5\" group=\"Article\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"reverseContent\" title=\"Reverse\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" value=\"6\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#0e0533\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"main-container\">\n                <div class=\"col-12 col-lg col-title\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showSubtitle\">\n                    <h5 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\"><div><b>Ethical Engagement As A Foundation For Trust</b></div></h5>\n                    <h6 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                        Ultricies mi quis hendrerit dolor magna eget.\n                    </h6>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}} col-text\">\n                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">Ethical engagement is not a side principle for Robert Susa; it is the foundation upon which clarity is built. Every service interaction is designed to be informative rather than persuasive. Inventors are encouraged to ask questions, seek understanding, and take ownership of their decisions.<br>\n<br>This ethical framework ensures that clarity is not just about information, but about intent. When inventors sense honesty and respect, they are more likely to engage thoughtfully with the process. Robert Susa’s commitment to ethical leadership reinforces this trust at every level.<br>\n<br>Over time, this approach strengthens confidence in invention services as a whole. It demonstrates that clarity and integrity are not obstacles to innovation but essential components of it.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor",
            "& when (@reverseContent)": {
              ".row": {
                "flex-direction": "row-reverse"
              }
            },
            ".main-container": {
              "display": "flex",
              "align-items": "stretch",
              "justify-content": "center",
              "padding": "0",
              "@media (max-width: 991px)": {
                "flex-wrap": "wrap",
                "padding": "0 40px"
              }
            },
            ".col-title, .col-text": {
              "display": "flex",
              "flex-direction": "column",
              "align-items": "stretch",
              "justify-content": "center",
              "padding": "10px"
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "color": "#ffffff",
              "margin-bottom": "0 !important",
              "@media (max-width: 767px)": {
                "text-align": "center !important"
              }
            },
            ".mbr-section-subtitle": {
              "color": "#112B6D",
              "margin-bottom": "0 !important",
              "margin-top": "20px",
              "@media (max-width: 767px)": {
                "text-align": "center !important"
              }
            },
            ".mbr-text": {
              "color": "#ffffff",
              "margin-bottom": "0.9rem !important",
              "@media (max-width: 767px)": {
                "text-align": "center !important"
              }
            }
          },
          "_cid": "v9v2E2cRcH",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {},
          "_anchor": "aarticle2-6l"
        },
        {
          "_name": "aarticle1",
          "_sourceTheme": "expertm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article1 expertm5\" group=\"Article\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <select title=\"Align\" name=\"contentAlign\">\n            <option value=\"justify-content-start\">Left</option>\n            <option value=\"justify-content-center\" selected>Center</option>\n            <option value=\"justify-content-end\">Right</option>\n        </select>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Content Width\" name=\"contentWidth\" min=\"6\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"11\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <header>Card Style</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card BG 1\" name=\"cardBg1\" value=\"#0e0533\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card BG 2\" name=\"cardBg2\" value=\"#0e0533\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"cardShadow\" title=\"Card Shadow\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Shadow Color 1\" name=\"shadowColor1\" value=\"#d6ee44\" condition=\"cardShadow\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Shadow Color 2\" name=\"shadowColor2\" value=\"#f6f420\" condition=\"cardShadow\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\">\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/expertm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/expertm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#212428\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.7\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row card-row {{contentAlign}}\">\n            <div class=\"item-card col-12 d-flex col-lg-{{contentWidth}}\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrap\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showText || showSubtitle\">\n                    <div class=\"row text-row align-items-center\">\n                        <div class=\"col-12\">\n                            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Continuous Refinement Through Education And Mentorship</b></h5>\n                            <h5 class=\"card-subtitle mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-subtitle\">\n                                Nulla malesuada pellentesque elit eget gravida cum sociis natoque penatibus.\n                                Tempor commodo ullamcorper a lacus vestibulum sed arcu non odio.\n                            </h5>\n                            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">Robert Susa’s dedication to clarity does not stop at established systems. He continually refines communication practices through education and mentorship. By investing in learning and professional development, he ensures that service explanations remain relevant, accurate, and effective.<br>\n<br>Mentorship plays a key role in maintaining clarity across the organization. Team members are guided not just on what to say, but on how to listen. This emphasis on two-way communication allows expectations to be adjusted thoughtfully when needed, without confusion or frustration.<br>\n<br>This ongoing refinement reflects a belief that clarity is dynamic. As inventors’ needs evolve, so too must the way services are explained and delivered.\n<br>\n<br></p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "& when (@bg-type = \"color\")": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = \"image\")": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)",
              "background-attachment": "fixed",
              "background-repeat": "no-repeat",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            "overflow": "hidden",
            ".item-wrap": {
              "position": "relative",
              "height": "100%",
              "width": "100%",
              "padding": "55px",
              "border-radius": "10px",
              "overflow": "hidden",
              "background": "linear-gradient(145deg, @cardBg1, @cardBg2)",
              "& when (@cardShadow)": {
                "box-shadow": "10px 10px 19px @shadowColor1, -10px -10px 19px @shadowColor2"
              },
              "@media (max-width: 767px)": {
                "padding": "40px"
              },
              "@media (max-width: 575px)": {
                "padding": "35px 25px 35px 25px"
              }
            },
            ".card-title": {
              "color": "#f4f5f7",
              "margin-bottom": "30px",
              "@media (max-width: 767px)": {
                "margin-bottom": "20px"
              }
            },
            ".card-subtitle": {
              "color": "#878e99",
              "margin-bottom": "30px",
              "@media (max-width: 767px)": {
                "margin-bottom": "20px"
              }
            },
            ".card-text": {
              "color": "#ffffff",
              "margin-bottom": "0"
            }
          },
          "_cid": "v9v2E3h7pz",
