          "_name": "content4",
          "_sourceTheme": "vibem5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content4 vibem5\" group=\"Content\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen, 'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Logo\" name=\"showLogo\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#000000\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-12\">\n                <div class=\"title-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"logo-wrap\" mbr-if=\"showLogo\">\n                        <img src=\"../_images/logo.png\" alt=\"Mobirise\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"title-wrap\">\n                        <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title, .mbr-section-btn, .logo-wrap\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><div>Robert Susa is widely recognized as a seasoned business leader whose career has been defined by principled leadership, ethical clarity, and a deep respect for the creative process. As President and Owner of InventHelp, a long-standing invention services organization, he has dedicated decades to supporting independent inventors as they navigate the often confusing journey from idea to commercialization. Rather than promoting quick wins or rushed outcomes, Robert Susa has consistently championed a more thoughtful, informed approach—one that places education at the very beginning of the innovation process.</div><br><div>\n</div><div>At the core of Robert Susa’s philosophy is the belief that inventors deserve to fully understand what they are stepping into before making decisions that could affect their ideas, finances, and long-term goals. His background in business development and organizational communications has shaped his ability to explain complex processes clearly and honestly. This skill has become a defining strength of his leadership, allowing him to foster transparency and trust at every stage of the invention journey.</div><br><div>\n</div><div>Under Robert Susa’s guidance, InventHelp’s services have been structured to empower inventors through knowledge. From patent referral services to prototype modeling and professional presentation materials, the organization emphasizes preparation and understanding rather than pressure. Inventors are encouraged to ask questions, explore options, and build confidence before moving forward. This educational foundation helps ensure that execution is purposeful, strategic, and aligned with realistic expectations.</div><br><div>\n</div><div>Beyond operational leadership, Robert Susa is deeply committed to mentorship and education as tools for long-term empowerment. He believes that when inventors are well-informed, they are better equipped to advocate for their ideas, communicate their value, and make sound decisions. This commitment to education before execution is not just a business strategy—it is a reflection of his broader professional ethos centered on integrity, respect, and shared success.\n</div><div><br></div></h2>\n                    </div>\n                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\">\n                        <a class=\"btn btn-primary-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                            Start Now\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "v9v2EuqTci",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {},
          "_anchor": "content4-6r"
        },
        {
          "_name": "article03",
          "_sourceTheme": "promotionm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article03 promotionm5\" group=\"Article\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Label\" name=\"showLabel\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Icon\" name=\"showIcon\" checked condition=\"showLabel\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/promotionm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#0e0533\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/promotionm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-10\">\n                <div class=\"content-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"row content-wrap\" mbr-class=\"{'flex-row-reverse' : reverseContent}\">\n                        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-3 card\">\n                            <div class=\"label-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showLabel\">\n                                <div class=\"label-wrap\">\n                                    <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                                        <span mbr-icon class=\"card-icon mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-more-horizontal mobi-mbri\" data-app-selector=\".card-icon\" style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); fill: rgb(31, 31, 31);\"></span>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-label mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-label, .label-wrapper\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                                        Elevate\n                                    </p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-9 card\">\n                            <div class=\"text-wrapper\">\n                                <div class=\"title-wrapper\">\n                                    <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title, .title-wrapper, .links-wrapper\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Robert Susa: Making Inventive Dreams Possible</b><br></h2>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"text-wrap\">\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .text-wrap\">For Robert Susa, innovation does not begin with action; it begins with understanding. Many inventors are driven by excitement and urgency, eager to see their ideas come to life. While that passion is essential, Robert Susa emphasizes that without education, enthusiasm can lead to missteps. Learning about the invention process, intellectual property basics, and realistic market considerations <a href=\"index.html\" class=\"text-primary\"><b><u>helps inventors</u></b></a> approach their ideas with confidence rather than guesswork.<br>\n<br>Education creates clarity. When inventors understand the steps involved, they are less likely to feel overwhelmed or discouraged later. Robert Susa’s approach ensures that inventors are not simply following instructions but actively participating in informed decision-making. This sense of ownership strengthens both confidence and commitment.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"links-wrapper\">\n                                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Brand Strategy\n                                        </a>\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Digital Marketing\n                                        </a>\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Content Creation\n                                        </a>\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Performance Analytics\n                                        </a>\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Social Media\n                                        </a>\n                                        <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                            Paid Advertising\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
